Package seedu.address.model.calendar

Interface ReadOnlyCalendar

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Calendar
    public interface ReadOnlyCalendar
    The interface for all getters and utilitiy methods. This is to prevent unwanted modifications to the existing calendar.
